== 製作 ==
=== 拍攝 ===
劇組定於4月10日在[[巴黎|巴黎]]開始進行拍攝<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/815635-christopher-mcquarrie-talks-mission-impossible-6-start-and-character-returns|title=Christopher McQuarrie Talks Mission: Impossible 6|date=2017-01-17|publisher=Comingsoon.net|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170523114324/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/815635-christopher-mcquarrie-talks-mission-impossible-6-start-and-character-returns|archivedate=2017-05-23|accessdate=2017-04-09}}</ref>。其他地點包括[[倫敦|倫敦]]、[[印度|印度]]和[[紐西蘭|紐西蘭]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://screenrant.com/mission-impossible-6-imax-3d/|title=Mission: Impossible 6 Shooting in IMAX 3D|date=2017-03-28|publisher=Screen Rant|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171023171404/http://screenrant.com/mission-impossible-6-imax-3d/|archivedate=2017-10-23|accessdate=2017-04-09}}</ref>。2017年4月8日，[[克里斯多福·麥奎里|克里斯多福·麥奎里]]宣布，拍攝正式於此日開始<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/chrismcquarrie/status/850609798144036864|title=Christopher McQuarrie on Twitter|access-date=2017-04-09|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112022127/https://twitter.com/chrismcquarrie/status/850609798144036864}}</ref>。電影主要使用35mm拍攝，部分場景使用雙機數位IMAX攝影機拍攝3D畫面。2017年7月，劇組移至紐西蘭拍攝<ref>{{cite news|last1=Evry|first1=Max|title=Mission: Impossible 6 Cast Photo as New Zealand Shoot Ends|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/866629-mission-impossible-6-cast-photo-as-new-zealand-filming-ends#/slide/1|accessdate=2017-07-10|work=ComingSoon.net|date=2017-07-10|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170711232317/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/866629-mission-impossible-6-cast-photo-as-new-zealand-filming-ends#/slide/1|archivedate=2017-07-11}}</ref>。9月20日至28日期間，挪威的[[布道台|布道台]]因拍攝工作而暫時關閉；僅劇組人員和演員才允許在山附近連續滯留九天。他們也每天允許多達五十架直升機著陸<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.dagbladet.no/kultur/tom-cruise-innspilling-pa-preikestolen-kan-skuffe-350-maratonlopere/68529816|title=Tom Cruise-innspilling på Preikestolen kan skuffe 350 maratonløpere|date=2017-06-21|publisher=dagbladet|accessdate=2017-08-18|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170818134231/https://www.dagbladet.no/kultur/tom-cruise-innspilling-pa-preikestolen-kan-skuffe-350-maratonlopere/68529816|archivedate=2017-08-18}}</ref>。2017年8月，克魯斯的右腿在倫敦拍攝時受了傷<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tmz.com/2017/08/13/tom-cruise-injured-mission-impossible-6-stunt/|title=Tom Cruise Injured in 'Mission Impossible 6' Stunt|work=[[TMZ|TMZ]]|date=2017-08-13|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180215073230/http://www.tmz.com/2017/08/13/tom-cruise-injured-mission-impossible-6-stunt/|archivedate=2018-02-15|accessdate=2017-08-18}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/la-et-entertainment-news-updates-august-tom-cruise-hurt-injured-mission-1502720227-htmlstory.html|title=Tom Cruise hurt filming 'Mission: Impossible 6' roof-jumping stunt|work=The Los Angeles Times|date=2017-08-14|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180221142355/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/la-et-entertainment-news-updates-august-tom-cruise-hurt-injured-mission-1502720227-htmlstory.html|archivedate=2018-02-21|accessdate=2017-08-18}}</ref>。事故發生後，劇組的工作至少停止了九個星期，以等待克魯斯的的腳踝和其他地方的傷康復；派拉蒙在事後發表聲明，電影的上映日仍維持在2018年7月<ref>{{cite news|last1=Jr|first1=Mike Fleming|title=Tom Cruise Stunt Injury Shuts Down ‘M:I 6 – Mission Impossible’|url=http://deadline.com/2017/08/tom-cruise-mission-impossible-stunt-injury-movie-shutdown-three-months-1202150039/|accessdate=2017-08-16|work=Deadline|date=2017-08-16|archive-date=2020-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200314224112/http://deadline.com/2017/08/tom-cruise-mission-impossible-stunt-injury-movie-shutdown-three-months-1202150039/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
《不可能的任務：全面瓦解》被[[派拉蒙影業|派拉蒙影業]]排於2018年7月27日在美國上映<ref name=ReleaseDateTHR>{{cite news|last1=McClintock|first1=Pamela|title=Tom Cruise's 'Mission: Impossible 6' Lands Summer 2018 Release Date|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/tom-cruises-mission-impossible-6-lands-summer-2018-release-date-945560|accessdate=2016-11-09|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2016-11-08|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161109225048/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/tom-cruises-mission-impossible-6-lands-summer-2018-release-date-945560|archivedate=2016-11-09}}</ref>。電影上映後，《{{link-en|詹姆斯柯登深夜秀|The Late Late Show with James Corden}}》主持[[詹姆斯·柯登|詹姆斯·柯登]]表示片中跳傘一幕屬小兒科，引來克魯斯親自帶他跳一次<ref name="MingPaoWeekly(2018-07-27)">{{cite news|url=https://bka.mpweekly.com/focus/foreign/20180727-124778|title=【超爆笑復仇】被名嘴笑新戲小兒科 靚佬湯捉佢玩跳傘|work=明周娛樂|date=2018-07-27|accessdate=2018-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180728101434/https://bka.mpweekly.com/focus/foreign/20180727-124778|archive-date=2018-07-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 評價 ===
《不可能的任務：全面瓦解》獲得了普遍正面的評價。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據406條評論，持有97%的新鮮度，平均得分8.36／10<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mission_impossible_fallout|title=Mission: Impossible - Fallout (2018)|work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|publisher=Fandango Media|accessdate=2018-07-12|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180712221032/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mission_impossible_fallout|archivedate=2018-07-12}}</ref>。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上，電影獲得了86分<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/mission-impossible-fallout|title=Mission: Impossible - Fallout Reviews|work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|accessdate=2018-07-12|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180712221308/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/mission-impossible-fallout|archivedate=2018-07-12}}</ref>。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾的迴響在A+至F間落於「A」<ref name="opening" />。

[[视与听|视与听]]的尼克·平克顿写道：「作为过去25年来最具影响力的系列电影的有力竞争者，《碟中谍》系列电影也提供了一个关于演员作为『电影作者（auteur）』的案例，[[汤姆·克鲁斯|汤姆·克鲁斯]]在《碟中谍6：全面瓦解》中继续将自己展现为银幕上无畏的不朽形象。」<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bfi.org.uk/news-opinion/sight-sound-magazine/features/tom-cruise-mission-impossible-franchise|title=Thrill of the Hunt: Tom Cruise and the Mission: Impossible franchise|publisher=Sight & Sound|accessdate=6 August 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180802012622/https://www.bfi.org.uk/news-opinion/sight-sound-magazine/features/tom-cruise-mission-impossible-franchise|archive-date=2018-08-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 票房 ===
北美方面，《不可能的任務：全面瓦解》與《[[電影少年悍將GO！|電影少年悍將GO！]]》同天上映並競爭，分析師預估前者在首映週末將獲得4800至6500萬美元的票房，有些媒體還高估至7500萬美元。該片於4386間戲院上映，成為系列之最及史上第七高的放映廳數<ref name="BOVariety" /><ref name="BOMproj" />。該片於週四晚間取得了600萬美元（包括來自IMAX放映廳的100萬美元），為系列最高，也對比《不可能的任務：失控國度》的400萬美元而成長了66%<ref>{{cite news |url=https://deadline.com/2018/07/tom-cruise-mission-impossible-fallout-opening-weekend-1202434739/ |title=‘Mission: Impossible – Fallout’ Beats ‘Rogue Nation’ Previews With $6M |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |publisher=Penske Business Media |date=2018-07-27 |first=Anthony |last=D'Alessandro |accessdate=2018-07-27 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/71MSFODW3?url=https://deadline.com/2018/07/tom-cruise-mission-impossible-fallout-opening-weekend-1202434739/ |archive-date=2018-08-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。該片於首週末開出6120萬美元的票房，為該系列最佳，以及克魯斯職業生涯中的第二高的成績，截至9/30止北美票房已突破2.2億美金，成為該系列票房冠軍。<ref name=opening>{{cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2018/07/tom-cruise-mission-impossible-fallout-opening-weekend-1202434739/ |title=‘Mission’ Accomplished: ‘Fallout’ $61M+ Opening Reps Record For Tom Cruise Franchise – Sunday |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |publisher=Penske Business Media |date=2018-07-29 |first=Anthony |last=D'Alessandro |accessdate=2018-07-29 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/71MSFODW3?url=https://deadline.com/2018/07/tom-cruise-mission-impossible-fallout-opening-weekend-1202434739/ |archive-date=2018-08-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://abcnews.go.com/Entertainment/wireStory/box-office-top-20-mission-impossible-hits-56927671|title=Box Office Top 20: New 'Mission: Impossible' hits No. 1|website=[[ABC_News|ABC News]]|publisher=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|date=2018-07-30|accessdate=2018-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180801094259/https://abcnews.go.com/Entertainment/wireStory/box-office-top-20-mission-impossible-hits-56927671|archive-date=2018-08-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

該片在第一天於海外市場上賺了1500萬美元，其中包括韓國的280萬美元<ref name="INTopen">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2018/07/mission-impossible-fallout-opening-weekend-international-box-office-china-date-1202435199/|title=‘Mission: Impossible – Fallout’ Lights Overseas Fuse With $15M; Sets China Date|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|publisher=Penske Business Media|date=2018-07-27|first=Nancy|last=Tartaglione|accessdate=2018-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180727213450/https://deadline.com/2018/07/mission-impossible-fallout-opening-weekend-international-box-office-china-date-1202435199/|archive-date=2018-07-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《不可能的任務：全面瓦解》於首週的全球票房為1.535億美元，其中海外佔了9200萬美元。其最大的市場為韓國（2460萬美元）、英國（900萬美元）和印度（700萬美元）<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2018/07/mission-impossible-fallout-opening-weekend-mamma-mia-incredibles-2-global-international-box-office-1202435956/|title=‘Mission: Impossible – Fallout’ Ignites Record $92M Overseas/$153.5M Global Bow – International Box Office|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|publisher=Penske Business Media|date=2018-07-29|first=Nancy|last=Tartaglione|accessdate=2018-07-30|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/71MS7zIxL?url=https://deadline.com/2018/07/mission-impossible-fallout-opening-weekend-mamma-mia-incredibles-2-global-international-box-office-1202435956/|archive-date=2018-08-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

